'''Al-Qurna Sport Club''' ({{lang-ar|'''نادي القرنة الرياضي'''}}), is an [[Iraq]]i football team based in [[Al-Qurna District|Al-Qurna]], [[Basra]], that plays in [[Iraq Division 1|Iraq Division one]].
