{{Multiple issues| {{primary sources|date=May 2016}}{{notability|Companies|date=May 2016}} {{Orphan|date=May 2016}} }} {{Infobox company | name = InfoKora | logo = File:Kco269Yz.png| | logo_size = 150px | logo_alt = InfoKora Logo as of 2016. | logo_caption = | logo_padding = | image = | image_size = | image_alt = | image_caption = | type = Private Held Company | founded = 2014 | hq_location = [[Cairo]], [[Egypt]] | industry = [[Sports media]] | products = Sports analysis | brands = http://www.123kora.com/ | services = | num_employees = 50 | num_employees_year = 2014 | parent = | slogan = | former_name = | website = http://www.infokora.com/ }}
'''INFOKORA''' is a [[football]] live score data provider headquartered in [[Cairo]], [[Egypt]].
Formed in 2014 by [[Egypt]]ian entrepreneur Haytham Amer, InfoKora analyses, covers and distributes live football data for over 4,000 fixtures{{clarify|reason=Fixtures? What word is intended here?|date=May 2016}} across 10 countries.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.linkedin.com/company/infokora|title=INFOKORA|website=www.linkedin.com|access-date=2016-05-08}}</ref> InfoKora data is used in print and online media, sponsorship, broadcasting and professional performance analysis. In May 2016, the company published a beta version of their first product, 123kora.com, a live score website available in English and Arabic. The site covers most of the Middle East football leagues, including [[Egyptian Premier League]], [[Saudi Professional League]], [[Qatar Stars League|QSL]] and [[Botola|Moroccan Botola]]; Europe's biggest leagues, including [[Premier League]], [[Ligue 1]], [[La Liga]], [[Serie A]], [[Bundesliga]] and [[UEFA Champions League|Champions League]].<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.123kora.com/|title=123Kora Home Page|website=www.123kora.com|access-date=2016-05-08}}</ref>
As of February 2016, the InfoKora [[Android (operating system)|Android]] app has reached 5,000 installs in the [[Google Play]] store.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.stats.Kora|title=123KORA Football Live Score - Android Apps on Google Play|website=play.google.com|access-date=2016-05-08}}</ref>
