'''Eskişehir Yeni Atatürk Stadyumu''' is a [[stadium]] [[Eskişehir]], [[Turkey]]. It opened to the public in late October 2016 and has a capacity of 34,930 spectators. It is the home ground of [[Eskişehirspor]]. It replaced the club's former home, [[Eskişehir Atatürk Stadium]].<ref>{{cite web|title=İşte Eskişehir’in yeni stadı|url=http://amkspor.com/2013/08/23/iste-eskisehirin-yeni-stadi-180969/|publisher=AMK SPOR|accessdate=23 June 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Eskişehir Yeni Stadyum İnşaatı|url=http://stadimiz.com/eskisehirspor-eskisehir-eses-arena-stat-insaatindan-resimler/|publisher=stadimiz.com|accessdate=23 June 2014}}</ref><ref>http://stadimiz.com/eskisehirspor-eskisehir-eses-arena-stat-insaatindan-resimler/</ref>
