Rwanda has never won an Olympic medal, but [[Jean de Dieu Nkundabera]] won a Paralympic bronze medal for Rwanda in [[Athletics at the 2004 Summer Paralympics|athletics]] at the [[2004 Summer Paralympics]] in [[Athens]].<ref>[http://goliath.ecnext.com/coms2/summary_0199-3521488_ITM "The Greek gods would be pleased--the 2004 Summer Paralympics revisited"], ''Palaestra'', September 22, 2004</ref>
